About Us
At Holiday Out, we pride ourselves on keeping our residents informed and connected through events and activities. We are proud of our community engagement, and through our website, keep everyone informed about area happenings, maintenance, events, and more.
Board of Directors
David Ganor – President
Joshua Watson – Vice-President
Mike Kemp – Secretary & Treasurer, Chair of Finance Committee
Fred Patterson- Chair of Legal and Rules
Dana Mullen – Chair of Recreation Committee
Ray Brumme – Chair of Building and Grounds Committee
Hal Camp – Volunteer Coordinator
Staff
Elaine Munson  (Property Manager) – manager@holidayout.org
(Front desk) – frontdesk
@holidayout.org
